    <para>
      Installez <application>Plasma-wayland-protocols</application> en lançant les
commandes suivantes&nbsp;:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr ..</userinput></screen>

